#: inc/admin-screens/options.php:71
msgid ""
"Each Avada Builder element can be enabled or disabled. This can increase "
"performance if you are not using a specific element. Check the box to "
"enable, uncheck to disable."
msgstr "每个 Avada 构建器元素都可以启用或禁用。如果您不使用特定元素，这可以提高性能。勾选以启用，取消勾选以禁用。"

#: inc/admin-screens/options.php:72
msgid ""
"<strong>NOTE:</strong> Elements for plugins like WooCommere or The Events "
"Calendar will only be available in the builder, if the corresponding options"
" are activated here and if those plugins are active."
msgstr ""
"<strong>注意：</strong>WooCommerce 或 The Events Calendar "
"等插件的元素只有在相应选项在此处被激活且这些插件处于活动状态时，才会在构建器中可用。"

#: inc/admin-screens/options.php:73
msgid ""
"<strong>WARNING:</strong> Use with caution. Disabling an element will remove"
" it from all pages/posts, old and new. If it was on a previous page/post, it"
" will render as regular element markup on the frontend."
msgstr ""
"<strong>警告：</strong>请谨慎使用。禁用元素将从所有页面/文章中移除它，无论新旧。如果它之前在某个页面/文章上，它将在前端呈现为常规元素标记。"

#: inc/admin-screens/options.php:75
msgid "Check All Elements"
msgstr "勾选所有元素"

#: inc/admin-screens/options.php:76
msgid "Uncheck All Elements"
msgstr "取消勾选所有元素"

#: inc/admin-screens/options.php:79
