"You can run an element scan which will scan for elements throughout your "
"site and uncheck any which are not used. <strong>WARNING:</strong> If your "
"website has a lot of content this may not run fully."
msgstr ""
"您可以运行元素扫描，它将扫描整个网站中的元素，并取消勾选未使用的元素。<strong>警告：</strong>如果您的网站内容很多，可能无法完全运行。"

#: inc/admin-screens/options.php:81
