#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:666
#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:747
#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:868
msgid ""
"If set to \"yes\", the password will be encrypted in any other form data "
"transmission, like saving to database or a notification email."
msgstr "如果设置为「是」，密码将在任何其他表单数据传输中加密，如保存到数据库或通知邮件。"

