msgstr "设置为「是」可在通知元素中添加额外的内部通知。"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:708
msgid ""
"Map fields from the form to the WordPress registration fields. To customize "
"the emails sent to admin and the new user use the %1$s and %2$s hook "
"respectively."
msgstr "将表单字段映射到 WordPress 注册字段。要自定义发送给管理员和新用户的邮件，请分别使用 %1$s 和 %2$s 钩子。"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:715
msgid ""
"Select the role for the new user. Administrator is disabled for security "
"reasons."
msgstr "选择新用户的角色。出于安全原因，管理员角色已被禁用。"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:722
msgid "Password Minimum Length"
msgstr "密码最小长度"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:723
msgid ""
"Set a minimum length for the password. Set to \"0\" to disable minimum "
"length. If the password is auto-created, the minimum length will always be "
"at least 12."
msgstr "设置密码的最小长度。设置为「0」可禁用最小长度限制。如果密码是自动创建的，最小长度将始终至少为 12。"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:735
msgid "Auto Create Username"
msgstr "自动创建用户名"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:736
msgid ""
"If set to \"yes\" and no username is specified in the form, the username "
"will be auto-created based on the given email address."
msgstr "如果设置为「是」且表单中未指定用户名，则将根据提供的邮箱地址自动创建用户名。"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:757
msgid "Auto Create Password"
msgstr "自动创建密码"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:758
msgid ""
"If set to \"yes\" and no password is specified in the form, the password "
"will be auto-created with respect to the minimum length option."
msgstr "如果设置为「是」且表单中未指定密码，则将根据最小长度选项自动创建密码。"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:768
msgid "Log In User"
msgstr "登录用户"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:769
msgid "Set to \"yes\" to log in the user after successful registration."
msgstr "设置为「是」可在注册成功后自动登录用户。"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:779
msgid "Send WordPress Notification"
msgstr "发送 WordPress 通知"

#: inc/class-fusion-form-auth-actions.php:780
msgid ""
"Send WordPress new user notification, by triggering the "
"\"register_new_user\" action."
msgstr "通过触发「register_new_user」操作发送 WordPress 新用户通知。"

