"Here you can manage critical CSS for your pages and posts.  Critical CSS is "
"the CSS necessary for above the fold styling. When critical CSS is available"
" the rest of the styles are deferred - leading to a faster render time."
msgstr ""
"在这里您可以管理页面和文章的关键 CSS。关键 CSS 是首屏样式所需的 CSS。当关键 CSS 可用时，其余样式将被延迟加载，从而加快渲染时间。"

#: inc/critical-css/class-awb-critical-css-page.php:660
