#: inc/critical-css/class-awb-critical-css-page.php:739
msgid ""
"This happens automatically, because after the theme has been updated, the "
"old CSS can cause artifacts on your pages. The best way is to regenerate all"
" critical css(using bulk actions from below), and then enable it."
msgstr ""
"这是自动发生的，因为主题更新后，旧的 CSS 可能会在您的页面上造成伪影。最好的方法是重新生成所有关键 CSS（使用下方的批量操作），然后启用它。"

